---
// src/components/AuthorBio.astro
---
<div class="author-bio">
  <div class="bio-avatar">
    <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="Po Hsieh" width="60" height="60" />
  </div>
  <div class="bio-content">
    <h3>Written by Po Hsieh</h3>
    <p>
      住院醫師 (Day) ⇄ 網頁開發者 (Night)。<br/>
      喜歡用程式碼解決臨床問題。
    </p>
    <div class="bio-links">
      <a href="/about">→ 關於我</a>
      <a href="/projects">→ 查看專案</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .author-bio {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .bio-avatar img {
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--card-bg);
  }
  .bio-content h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .bio-content p {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .bio-links a {
    margin-right: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
</style>